name: XAct
tagline: Swift numerics, maths, data structures, algorithms and machine learning.
body:
A comprehensive Swift framework library containing numerical algorithms, mathematical functions, data structures, machine learning algorithms, data generators and more.

The library is ported from the [Numerics library for .Net](https://github.com/Orbifold/Numerics) and is part of [Orbifold's consultancy](http://www.orbifold.net) toolbox.
